OL,3,CWoman dies after reports of
OL,4,C'explosion' at house
OL,6,FA woman has died after a fire at a
OL,7,Fhouse in Chippenham.
OL,9,FWiltshire Police said emergency
OL,10,Fservices were called to reports of an
OL,11,Fexplosion at an address on Orchard
OL,12,FCrescent at about 3.30pm on 5 March.
OL,14,FA woman in her 40s was found dead at
OL,15,Fthe scene.
OL,17,FThe 'explosion' which was reported to
OL,18,Fthe emergency services was found to be
OL,19,Fa patio slab which had overheated and
OL,20,Fcracked due to a fire at the address,
OL,21,Fpolice say.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
