OL,3,CWoman dies after reports of
OL,4,C'explosion' at house
OL,6,FOfficers say the woman's next of kin
OL,7,Fhave been informed and there are not
OL,8,Fbelieved to be any suspicious
OL,9,Fcircumstances around her death.
